{"tid":583183,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"九巴暫緩解僱決定 4車長將循機制上訴 (4:15)","createTime":"2018-03-06T20:40:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-08T11:34:32.000Z","uid":27797,"like":13,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"6276a6f741a318020bc71b7ecc3af91a0b6bc1bc","tid":583183,"uid":27797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T20:40:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1055577\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1055577&d=oIln4n8eGtpJdUtBmG8i3p4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=6ee41863\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1055577&h=813474e7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1055577</a><br />\n<br />\n九巴暫緩解僱決定 4車長將循機制上訴 (4:15)<br />\n<br />\n（獨媒特約報導）接近凌晨兩點，月薪車長大聯盟召集人葉蔚琳表示，將即時會見九巴總經理蘇偉基，爭取4名車長先復職，希望能在復職後再和九巴對話爭取改善待遇。<br />\n<br />\n會面進行超過1小時，近凌晨4時，葉蔚琳表示感謝傳媒和聲援的市民，蘇偉基表示4人今天能取回工作證，目前是先恢復僱員身份，並會透過制度提出上訴。<br />\n<br />\n葉蔚琳續稱，早前提出的三個訴求都獲得九巴考慮，包括極大可能取消評核制度，九巴會盡快推出措施減低乘客與車長磨擦，而工會將繼續爭取公平對話機制。但葉指目前會先通過制度作上訴。她又再次感謝市民的支持，「團結就是力量」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n月薪車長大聯盟召集人葉蔚琳<br />\n<br />\n九巴傳訊部副主管林子豪則稱，暫緩終止4名車長僱傭關係的決定，而覆檢程式會盡快進行，重申稱是根據既有程序，車長提出上訴因此必須暫緩決定。<br />\n<br />\n巴士業職工會聯盟今日中午12時半到九巴母公司新鴻基集團抗議。職工盟秘書長李卓人表示，今日只是開始，必須繼續關注，直至正式復職及待遇得到改善。<br />\n<br />\n九巴傳訊部副主管林子豪<br />\n<br />\n記者：麥馬高"},{"pid":"7f29a586940fc2707a1a7b52171c7cee41932fd3","tid":583183,"uid":27797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T20:46:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f988b88bbf05541d42b0fdbb972910f28b8a96d1","tid":583183,"uid":27797,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T21:07:40.000Z","msg":"無人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"686b9dc636f43e272398bad3f1f4814054d4cfcd","tid":583183,"uid":54884,"like":5,"dislike":20,"score":-15,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T21:09:26.000Z","msg":"九巴做咩咁驚 根本唔會有事 罷工炒人係好合理"},{"pid":"aadbdb286ac2d141a1901b8f432c9b58f710a07b","tid":583183,"uid":33908,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"686b9dc636f43e272398bad3f1f4814054d4cfcd","tid":583183,"uid":54884,"like":5,"dislike":20,"score":-15,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T21:09:26.000Z","msg":"九巴做咩咁驚 根本唔會有事 罷工炒人係好合理"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T21:21:01.000Z","msg":"拖長件事.慢慢就會無人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"932864ef37796d1f4903f4c7a5a6580fdf50a75a","tid":583183,"uid":29514,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"f988b88bbf05541d42b0fdbb972910f28b8a96d1","tid":583183,"uid":27797,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T21:07:40.000Z","msg":"無人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T21:21:27.000Z","msg":"而家幾點啊ching<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c01589d678da814074ecb7a8cc3b587df30af46","tid":583183,"uid":119478,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T21:22:48.000Z","msg":"之後劇本<br />\n上訴得直-&gt;車長加薪-&gt;加價"},{"pid":"0982152b8c87f83bf461a1c41fd30efb511dbb19","tid":583183,"uid":151774,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T21:42:24.000Z","msg":"兩雞嘢都無 炒咪炒囉 好撚閒姐<br />\n點解死都要爭取繼續做？<br />\n你話月薪3雞以上就話爭取下留職姐"},{"pid":"80c36240edb6ad6b1fa69b23b738370190ed2a97","tid":583183,"uid":72280,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"8c01589d678da814074ecb7a8cc3b587df30af46","tid":583183,"uid":119478,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T21:22:48.000Z","msg":"之後劇本<br />\n上訴得直-&gt;車長加薪-&gt;加價"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T22:10:22.000Z","msg":"暫緩只是合理化死因的必經階段<br />\n務求程序正義<br />\n<br />\n新聞片+現場拍的片都用曬黎做 record <br />\n再加埋口供紙同 現場人員interview <br />\n其實好難打得甩<br />\n<br />\n利申：阿叔報夢話我聽"},{"pid":"61af60287fe67c3348a9fa02d2ea9ddedc507fcc","tid":583183,"uid":35730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"201